com.paypal.merchant.sdk.domain
Interface Address

public interface Address

The address object allows the Address info to be formatted and
organized in a way that makes it easier to extract specific info
such as city, state fields - that maybe needed for requests sent
to the backend.

The Address object follows the pattern of using a Builder class
to facilitate the creation of an object and the class itself contains
getters that the application or any other entity to pull in whatever
fields may be interesting to their needs.

Nested Class Summary
static interface Address.Builder
          A builder interface that provides an easy to set the various fields.
